Class FlipFitAdminBusiness

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.business.FlipFitAdminBusiness
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFlipFitAdmin
public class FlipFitAdminBusiness extends Object implements IFlipFitAdmin
Business logic for managing FlipFit Admin operations. Implements functionality for admin login, owner validation, user management, and gym centre management.
